Get UNCTAD data

get_unctad.Rd

Get UNCTAD data

Usage

get_unctad(file)

Arguments

file

An UNCTAD 7zip download file (see url_unctad() for where to get it)

Value

A tibble of UNCTAD commodity price data

See also

Other UNCTAD: acquire_unctad(), get_unctad_metadata(), url_unctad()

Examples


a <- system.file("extdata", "unctad-example.csv.7z", package = "fsp")
a
#> [1] "/home/runner/work/_temp/Library/fsp/extdata/unctad-example.csv.7z"
get_unctad(a)
